{{Politics of Sri Lanka}}

'''{{le|第16届斯里兰卡议会|16th Parliament of Sri Lanka|第16届}}[[斯里兰卡议会|斯里兰卡议会]]选举'''于2020年8月5日举行，选出新一届议会225个议席<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/03/sri-lankan-parliament-dissolved-elections-set-april-200302193858515.html|title=Sri Lankan parliament dissolved; elections set for April|publisher=Al Jazeera|access-date=2020-03-16|archive-date=2020-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312191710/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/03/sri-lankan-parliament-dissolved-elections-set-april-200302193858515.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.msn.com/en-xl/news/other/general-election-will-be-held-on-june-20/ar-BB12VUiK|title=General Election will be held on June 20|publisher=MSN|accessdate=2020-08-11|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705084126/https://www.msn.com/en-xl/news/other/general-election-will-be-held-on-june-20/ar-BB12VUiK|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-05|title=Sri Lanka general elections 2020 – LIVE UPDATES|url=https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-general-elections-2020-live-updates-72653,%20https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-general-elections-2020-live-updates-72653/|access-date=2020-08-06|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。本届共有16,263,885名符合资格的选民，其中青年选民占31.95%<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-07-29|title=Over 1.2 million new votes registered for Sri Lanka’s upcoming polls|url=https://economynext.com/over-1-2-million-new-votes-registered-for-sri-lankas-upcoming-polls-72471,%20https://economynext.com/over-1-2-million-new-votes-registered-for-sri-lankas-upcoming-polls-72471/|access-date=2020-08-06|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-07-28|title=Sri Lanka’s youth are unlikely to vote for the old guard in Parliament|url=https://economynext.com/sri-lankas-youth-are-unlikely-to-vote-for-the-old-guard-in-parliament-72422,%20https://economynext.com/sri-lankas-youth-are-unlikely-to-vote-for-the-old-guard-in-parliament-72422/|access-date=2020-08-06|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

执政联盟[[斯里兰卡人民自由联盟|斯里兰卡人民自由联盟]]凭借145个议席的压倒性胜利胜选<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rajapaksas dominates South with landslide victory in Sri Lankan elections {{!}} Tamil Guardian|url=https://www.tamilguardian.com/content/rajapaksas-dominates-south-landslide-victory-sri-lankan-elections|access-date=2020-08-07|website=www.tamilguardian.com|archive-date=2022-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220407090314/https://www.tamilguardian.com/content/rajapaksas-dominates-south-landslide-victory-sri-lankan-elections}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=CNN|first=Iqbal Athas and Helen Regan|title=Sri Lanka's Mahinda Rajapaksa declares victory in parliamentary elections|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/08/07/asia/sri-lanka-election-mahinda-rajapaksa-intl-hnk/index.html|access-date=2020-08-07|website=CNN|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807100033/https://www.cnn.com/2020/08/07/asia/sri-lanka-election-mahinda-rajapaksa-intl-hnk/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-07|title=Sri Lanka Podujana Party wins 2020 general elections in a landslide|url=https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-podujana-party-wins-2020-general-elections-in-a-landslide-72732,%20https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-podujana-party-wins-2020-general-elections-in-a-landslide-72732/|access-date=2020-08-07|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>，其后是赢得54个议席的{{le|团结—人民力量|Samagi Jana Balawegaya}}和3个[[人民解放阵线_(斯里兰卡)|人民解放阵线]]<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-08-07|title=Rajapaksa declares election victory in Sri Lanka|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53688584|access-date=2020-08-07|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807044428/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53688584|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka : 2020 Parliamentary Election Results: SLPP wins six seats in Matara district, SJB one|url=http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug06_1596723489CH.php|access-date=2020-08-07|website=www.colombopage.com|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809000029/http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug06_1596723489CH.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Rajapaksa brothers win by landslide in Sri Lanka's election|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/rajapaksa-brothers-win-landslide-sri-lanka-election-200807025501325.html|access-date=2020-08-07|website=www.aljazeera.com|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807032513/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/rajapaksa-brothers-win-landslide-sri-lanka-election-200807025501325.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主要反对党[[统一国民党|统一国民党]]领导层分裂之后，经历了历史上最糟糕的表现，仅获得1个席位，位列第四<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-06|title=Sri Lanka ex-PM’s UNP polls less than 5-pct in declared Colombo seats|url=https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-ex-pms-unp-polls-less-than-5-pct-in-declared-colombo-seats-72725,%20https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-ex-pms-unp-polls-less-than-5-pct-in-declared-colombo-seats-72725/|access-date=2020-08-07|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

受{{le|2019冠状病毒病斯里兰卡疫情|COVID-19 pandemic in Sri Lanka|2019冠状病毒病疫情}}肆虐影响，选举时间两度推迟，最终确定为2020年8月5日<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-06-21|title=Sri Lanka prepares for twice-delayed poll amid militarized COVID-19 response · Global Voices|url=https://globalvoices.org/2020/06/21/sri-lanka-prepares-for-twice-delayed-poll-amid-militarized-covid-19-response/|access-date=2020-08-06|website=Global Voices|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731100437/https://globalvoices.org/2020/06/21/sri-lanka-prepares-for-twice-delayed-poll-amid-militarized-covid-19-response/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Srinivasan|first=Meera|date=2020-07-13|title=Lanka election body ‘monitoring’ virus spike|language=en-IN|work=The Hindu|url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/lanka-election-body-monitoring-virus-spike/article32071512.ece|access-date=2020-08-07|issn=0971-751X|archive-date=2020-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721171349/https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/lanka-election-body-monitoring-virus-spike/article32071512.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。选举前夕，中央选举委员会按照健康指南的要求，于6月举行了[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]防控的模拟选举<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-06-14|title=Sri Lanka holds coronavirus-proof test vote|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53042755|access-date=2020-08-06|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705130455/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53042755|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka to conduct advance polling for people under quarantine|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/world/2020/jul/26/sri-lanka-to-conduct-advance-polling-for-people-under-quarantine-2175058.html|access-date=2020-08-07|website=The New Indian Express|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729063540/https://www.newindianexpress.com/world/2020/jul/26/sri-lanka-to-conduct-advance-polling-for-people-under-quarantine-2175058.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

最初的报道估计整体投票率为70％，较{{tsl|en|2015 Sri Lankan parliamentary election|2015年斯里兰卡议会选举|上一届}}有所下降，主要是疫情所致<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-06|title=Sri Lanka 2020 general elections turnout lower, steepest in Kurunegala|url=https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-2020-general-elections-turnout-lower-steepest-in-kurunegala-72679,%20https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-2020-general-elections-turnout-lower-steepest-in-kurunegala-72679/|access-date=2020-08-06|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。计票工作于8月6日上午9时许启动<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka counts votes from parliamentary elections|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/sri-lanka-counts-votes-parliamentary-elections-200806051340624.html|access-date=2020-08-06|website=www.aljazeera.com|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806062656/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/sri-lanka-counts-votes-parliamentary-elections-200806051340624.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新一届议会预计于2020年8月20日重新召开<ref>{{Cite web|title=New Parliament to meet on August 20|url=http://www.dailynews.lk/2020/08/04/political/225050/new-parliament-meet-august-20|access-date=2020-08-06|website=Daily News|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806231515/http://www.dailynews.lk/2020/08/04/political/225050/new-parliament-meet-august-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-04|title=New Parliament to meet on 20th of August 2020|url=https://www.newsfirst.lk/2020/08/04/new-parliament-to-meet-on-20th-of-august-2020/|access-date=2020-08-07|website=Sri Lanka News – Newsfirst|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220404002346/https://www.newsfirst.lk/2020/08/04/new-parliament-to-meet-on-20th-of-august-2020/}}</ref>。

2018年11月，总统[[邁特里帕拉·西里塞納|邁特里帕拉·西里塞納]]在[[2018年斯里蘭卡憲法危機|宪政危机]]中解散议会后，曾要求提前举行大选，计划将议会选举提前一年至2019年1月5日举行<ref name="parliamentdissolved">{{cite news |last1=Bastians |first1=Dharisha |last2=Goel |first2=Vindu |title=Sri Lanka President Dissolves Parliament Amid Power Struggle |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/11/09/world/asia/sri-lanka-dissolves-parliament.html |accessdate=2018-11-26 |work=The New York Times |date=2018-11-09 |archive-date=2018-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109202613/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/11/09/world/asia/sri-lanka-dissolves-parliament.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最高法院后来驳回该决议，要求暂缓大选，将议会选举的日期恢复至2020年<ref>{{cite news|title=Sri Lanka Supreme Court overturns dissolution of parliament|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/11/sri-lanka-supreme-court-overturns-dissolution-parliament-181113125340789.html|accessdate=2018-11-26|agency=Al Jazeera and news agencies|date=2018-11-13|archive-date=2018-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181114005400/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/11/sri-lanka-supreme-court-overturns-dissolution-parliament-181113125340789.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
2018年[[2018年斯里蘭卡憲法危機|宪法危机]]期间，[[戈塔巴雅·拉贾帕克萨|戈塔巴雅·拉贾帕克萨]]解散议会并要求大选，提名马欣达·拉贾帕克萨出任总理，但该提名未获得议会大多数支持<ref name="parliamentdissolved" />。

然而，[[斯里兰卡最高法院|斯里兰卡最高法院]]认为解散议会不符合宪法，暂缓解散，大选的提前也因为司法案件正在处理而暂缓。2018年12月13日，最高法院裁定解散议会不符合宪法，将选举时间恢复到原定日期<ref>{{cite news |last1=Rasheed |first1=Zaheena |last2=Kuruwita |first2=Rathindra |title=Sri Lanka's Supreme Court overturns sacking of parliament |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/12/sri-lanka-supreme-court-overturns-sacking-parliament-181213113720319.html |accessdate=2018-12-14 |publisher=Al Jazeera |date=2018-12-13 |archive-date=2018-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213211924/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/12/sri-lanka-supreme-court-overturns-sacking-parliament-181213113720319.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年5月19日，选举委员会考虑到2019冠状病毒病疫情推迟选举，但未宣布新日期<ref name="auto">{{cite web | title=Sri Lanka's General Election postponed | website=Adaderana | url=http://www.adaderana.lk/news/61545/sri-lankas-general-election-postponed | access-date=2020-06-15 | archive-date=2020-04-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412213344/http://www.adaderana.lk/news/61545/sri-lankas-general-election-postponed | dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月20日，选举委员会通知最高法院澄清选举的具体日期为2020年6月20日<ref name="#1">[https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2020/05/20/world/asia/ap-as-sri-lanka-election.html]{{dead link|date=June 2020}}</ref>。6月10日，选举委员马欣达·德沙普里亚确认推迟的议会选举将在8月5日举行。7月17日，经过长时间的拖延，{{tsl|en|Ministry of Health, Nutrition and Indigenous Medicine|卫生、营养与原住民医学部}}就选举卫生指南发布公报<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka : Sri Lanka election monitor expresses concern over changing COVID-19 health guidelines for election campaigning|url=http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Jul19_1595175794CH.php|access-date=2020-08-05|website=www.colombopage.com|archive-date=2020-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721000004/http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Jul19_1595175794CH.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===COVID-19疫情===
{{Main|{{le|2019冠状病毒病斯里兰卡疫情|COVID-19 pandemic in Sri Lanka}}}}
2020年3月19日，斯里兰卡包括[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]病例数有所增加，但政府继续直到3月18日结束的选举提名期<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20A/Mar19_1584592211CH.php|title=Sri Lanka : Curfew in Puttalam area lifted temporarily for nomination process|website=colombopage.com|accessdate=2020-08-11|archive-date=2020-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412214137/http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20A/Mar19_1584592211CH.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月19日，提名期结束后不久，选举委员会行使权力推迟选举<ref name="auto"/>。推迟日期最初定为4月25日，之后再因疫情推迟到6月20日，之后再推迟至最终日期。斯里兰卡因此与波兰、韩国、新加坡、叙利亚和塞尔维亚一道成为在疫情期间举行选举的国家<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-02|title=Sri Lanka gears up for delayed polls amid pandemic|url=https://arab.news/vmeda|access-date=2020-08-05|website=Arab News|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-03|title=Sri Lanka’s parliamentary elections will hold lessons for India’s Election Commission ahead of Bihar polls|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/opinion/columns/sri-lanka-coronavirus-elections-6536509/|access-date=2020-08-05|website=The Indian Express|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804024424/https://indianexpress.com/article/opinion/columns/sri-lanka-coronavirus-elections-6536509/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是首个在疫情期间举行选举的南亚国家<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka's parliamentary elections: Five things to know|url=https://asia.nikkei.com/Politics/Sri-Lanka-s-parliamentary-elections-Five-things-to-know|access-date=2020-08-05|website=Nikkei Asian Review|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804130745/https://asia.nikkei.com/Politics/Sri-Lanka-s-parliamentary-elections-Five-things-to-know|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

卫生官员就选民安全作出特别安排，在选举之前用消毒剂对投票站（包括投票站的内部和外部摊位）进行消毒<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka : All polling centers to be disinfected today and tomorrow|url=http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug03_1596460809CH.php|access-date=2020-08-05|website=www.colombopage.com|archive-date=2022-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220402171032/http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug03_1596460809CH.php}}</ref>。

==选举制度==
是次选举通过22个多议员{{tsl|en|Electoral districts in Sri Lanka|斯里兰卡选区|选区}}选出196名议员，采用[[漢狄法|漢狄法]]及[[開放名單|開放名單]][[比例代表制|比例代表制]]制度<ref>{{cite book|last1=Blanc|first1=Jarrett|last2=Hylland|first2=Aanund|last3=Vollan|first3=Kare|title=State Structure and Electoral Systems in Post-Conflict Situations|date=2006|publisher=International Foundation for Electoral Systems]isbn=1-931459-17-7|page=106|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1EXgwebG5oEC|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417195140/https://books.google.com/books?id=1EXgwebG5oEC|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Report of the Post-Election Assessment of Sri Lanka Mission: November 28 – December 2, 2000|url=https://www.ndi.org/files/1198_lk_postelect122000.pdf|publisher=National Democratic Institute for International Affairs|page=10|date=2000-12-28|access-date=2018-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232543/https://www.ndi.org/files/1198_lk_postelect122000.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。余下29个议席由参选的[[斯里兰卡政党列表|各政党]]和[[无党籍|无党籍]]组织按照全国得票份额比分配<ref>{{cite book|last1=Thilakarathne|first1=N. M. C.|editor1-last=Brian|editor1-first=Rob|title=Parliamentary Libraries and Information Services of Asia and the Pacific: Papers prepared for the 62nd IFLA Conference Beijing, China August 25–31, 1996|date=1997|publisher=Walter de Gruyte|isbn=3-11-094763-3|page=87|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rlohAAAAQBAJ|chapter=Parliament Library of Sri Lanka|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405035153/https://books.google.com/books?id=rlohAAAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sri Lanka: Parliament|url=http://www.ipu.org/parline/reports/2295.htm|publisher=Inter-Parliamentary Union|accessdate=2020-08-11|archive-date=2017-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408010551/http://www.ipu.org/parline/reports/2295.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。选举委员会宣布选票可以投票给一个主要政党，最多可以选出3个人进行排序投票<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-04|title=Sri Lanka electors can vote for one party, three preferences in 2020 general elections: polls chief|url=https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-electors-can-vote-for-one-party-three-preferences-in-2020-general-elections-polls-chief-72625,%20https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-electors-can-vote-for-one-party-three-preferences-in-2020-general-elections-polls-chief-72625/|access-date=2020-08-05|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

== 参选政党 ==
参与选举的主要政党和联盟包括总统戈塔巴雅·拉贾帕克萨联盟、执政党[[斯里兰卡人民自由联盟|斯里兰卡人民自由联盟]]、[[拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈|拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈]]的主要反对党[[统一国民党|统一国民党]]、{{tsl|en|Sajith Premadasa|萨吉斯·普里马达萨}}的{{tsl|en|Samagi Jana Balawegaya|团结—人民力量}}、[[阿努拉·库马拉·迪萨纳亚克|阿努拉·库马拉·迪萨纳亚克]]的[[人民解放阵线_(斯里兰卡)|人民解放阵线]]。总统戈塔巴雅此前于2019年11月当选总统。

统一国民党的独立派系团结—人民力量由萨吉斯·普里马达萨于2020年2月成立，当时萨吉斯和拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈就统一国民党的存在仇隙，就领导问题产生创意分歧<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-07-29|title=Sacking pro-SJB members from the UNP “was long overdue” – Asst. Leader RaviK|url=https://economynext.com/sacking-pro-sjb-members-from-the-unp-was-long-overdue-asst-leader-ravik-72472,%20https://economynext.com/sacking-pro-sjb-members-from-the-unp-was-long-overdue-asst-leader-ravik-72472/|access-date=2020-08-07|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Abhayasinghe|first=Shiromi|title=SJB is a separate party – Ranil|url=http://www.dailynews.lk/2020/07/25/political/224301/sjb-separate-party-ranil|access-date=2020-08-07|website=Daily News|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728111853/http://www.dailynews.lk/2020/07/25/political/224301/sjb-separate-party-ranil|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The UNP, SJB and intra-party democracy {{!}} Daily FT|url=http://www.ft.lk/columns/The-UNP--SJB-and-intra-party-democracy/4-703123|access-date=2020-08-07|website=www.ft.lk|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716035259/http://www.ft.lk/columns/The-UNP--SJB-and-intra-party-democracy/4-703123|dead-url=no}}</ref>。虽然刚刚成立，该党仍自称是主要反对党<ref>{{Cite web|title=SJB commits to people centric governance {{!}} Daily FT|url=http://www.ft.lk/top-story/SJB-commits-to-people-centric-governance/26-703445|access-date=2020-08-07|website=www.ft.lk|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722120830/http://www.ft.lk/top-story/SJB-commits-to-people-centric-governance/26-703445|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 发展 ==
2020年3月19日，选举委员会主席{{tsl|en|Mahinda Deshapriya|马欣达·德沙普里亚}}透露，鉴于[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]，选举无限期推迟<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://newsin.asia/sri-lankas-general-election-postponed/|title=Sri Lanka’s General Election postponed till country is freed from COVID-19|date=2020-03-19|website=NewsIn.Asia|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-19|archive-date=2020-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319161732/https://newsin.asia/sri-lankas-general-election-postponed/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.asiantribune.com/node/93497|title=Sri Lanka’s General Election postponed: Until the polls Country comes under Election Commission {{!}} Asian Tribune|website=www.asiantribune.com|access-date=2020-03-19|archive-date=2020-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319161742/http://www.asiantribune.com/node/93497|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。斯里兰卡政府最初坚持定于举行的选举于4月25日按原计划举行，但禁止竞选集会和会议<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://colombogazette.com/2020/03/15/president-tells-saarc-leaders-april-election-will-go-ahead/|title=President tells SAARC leaders April election will go ahead|last=admin|date=2020-03-15|website=Colombo Gazette|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-03-16|archive-date=2020-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319162201/https://colombogazette.com/2020/03/15/president-tells-saarc-leaders-april-election-will-go-ahead/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在与其他[[南亚区域合作联盟|南亚区域合作联盟]]领导人举行视频会议时，斯里兰卡总统戈塔巴雅·拉贾帕克萨确认选举按原计划举行<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://menafn.com/1099857379/Sri-Lanka-President-tells-SAARC-leaders-April-election-will-go-ahead|title=Sri Lanka- President tells SAARC leaders April election will go ahead|last=MENAFN|website=menafn.com|access-date=2020-03-16|archive-date=2022-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220409115744/https://menafn.com/1099857379/Sri-Lanka-President-tells-SAARC-leaders-April-election-will-go-ahead}}</ref>。尽管总统表示选举照常举行，选举委员会还当用权力将日期推迟到6月20日<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/sri-lanka-quandary-over-holding-100322893.html|title=Sri Lanka election set for June 20, ending possible crisis|publisher=Yahoo!|accessdate=2020-08-11|archive-date=2020-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607081315/https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/sri-lanka-quandary-over-holding-100322893.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这导致总统办公室与宪法产生危机，事件交由法庭裁决<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.outlookindia.com/newsscroll/sri-lankan-supreme-court-told-parliamentary-election-can-be-held-on-june-20-under-health-guidelines/1843135|title=Sri Lankan Supreme Court told parliamentary election can be held on June 20 under health guidelines|website=outlookindia.com|access-date=2020-08-11|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511232720/https://www.outlookindia.com/newsscroll/sri-lankan-supreme-court-told-parliamentary-election-can-be-held-on-june-20-under-health-guidelines/1843135}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://wtop.com/asia/2020/04/sri-lanka-in-quandary-over-holding-elections-amid-virus/|title=Sri Lanka election set for June 20, ending possible crisis|date=2020-04-20|publisher=WTOP|accessdate=2020-08-11|archive-date=2020-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426210823/https://wtop.com/asia/2020/04/sri-lanka-in-quandary-over-holding-elections-amid-virus/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

6月10日，选举委员马欣达·德沙普里亚确认议会选举推迟至8月5日举行，需遵循严格的健康措施和指引<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-06-10|title=Sri Lanka's parliamentary elections fixed for August 5|url=https://www.newsfirst.lk/2020/06/10/general-election-on-august-5/|access-date=2020-06-10|website=Sri Lanka News – Newsfirst|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610122015/https://www.newsfirst.lk/2020/06/10/general-election-on-august-5/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-06-10|title=Sri Lanka Parliamentary General Election to be held on Aug 5|url=https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-parliamentary-general-election-to-be-held-on-aug-5-70930,%20https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-parliamentary-general-election-to-be-held-on-aug-5-70930/|access-date=2020-06-10|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link|date=2020年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Sri Lanka's General Election on August 05 | website=Adaderana | url=http://www.adaderana.lk/news.php?nid=64554 | access-date=2020-06-15 | archive-date=2020-06-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613153232/http://www.adaderana.lk/news.php?nid=64554 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

多方消息来源认为，由于病毒令人担忧，初期投票率会进展缓慢，但到了清晨会逐渐回升<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-05|title=Sri Lanka general election voting picking up after slow start, Colombo 26-pct: officials: officials|url=https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-general-election-voting-picking-up-after-slow-start-colombo-26-pct-officials-officials-72644,%20https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-general-election-voting-picking-up-after-slow-start-colombo-26-pct-officials-officials-72644/|access-date=2020-08-05|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka : Polling begins for Sri Lanka parliamentary elections amid coronavirus fears|url=http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug05_1596599154CH.php|access-date=2020-08-05|website=www.colombopage.com|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807015915/http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug05_1596599154CH.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是斯里兰卡首次在疾病疫情期间举行大选<ref>{{Cite web|title=Poetry for reflection on Sri Lanka’s Election Day {{!}} Daily FT|url=http://www.ft.lk/columns/Poetry-for-reflection-on-Sri-Lanka-s-Election-Day/4-704084|access-date=2020-08-08|website=www.ft.lk|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808151207/http://www.ft.lk/columns/Poetry-for-reflection-on-Sri-Lanka-s-Election-Day/4-704084|dead-url=no}}</ref>，选举委员会建议选民自带蓝色或黑色[[原子笔|原子笔]]，遵循预防性保持距离指南迅速完成投票<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-05|title=Stay apart and bring a pen: Sri Lanka goes to the polls during pandemic|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/05/sri-lanka-election-vote-coronavirus-rajapaksa|access-date=2020-08-05|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805055551/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/05/sri-lanka-election-vote-coronavirus-rajapaksa|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=MENAFN|title=Sri Lanka- Voters permitted to use their own pens at polls|url=https://menafn.com/1100575998/Sri-Lanka-Voters-permitted-to-use-their-own-pens-at-polls|access-date=2020-08-05|website=menafn.com|archive-date=2022-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220409032738/https://menafn.com/1100575998/Sri-Lanka-Voters-permitted-to-use-their-own-pens-at-polls}}</ref>。官方也建议选民佩戴口罩，在进出投票站时用[[消毒搓手液|消毒搓手液]]消毒<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka's election chief assures voter safety on eve of parliamentary election – Xinhua {{!}} English.news.cn|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-08/04/c_139264855.htm|access-date=2020-08-05|website=www.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805050018/http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-08/04/c_139264855.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=5 Aug|first=Reuters {{!}}|last2=2020|last3=Ist|first3=09:39|title=Sri Lanka Parliamentary Elections 2020: Sri Lankans, wearing masks, flock to voting centres for parliament election {{!}} World News – Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lankans-wearing-masks-flock-to-voting-centres-for-parliament-election/articleshow/77364026.cms|access-date=2020-08-05|website=The Times of India|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806053920/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lankans-wearing-masks-flock-to-voting-centres-for-parliament-election/articleshow/77364026.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

投票当天，选举主席马欣达·德沙普里亚在巡视投票站时投票，而非选择邮寄投票。这是他九年来首次现身投票站<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-05|title=Sri Lanka Elections Commissioner casts vote at polling station after 9 years|url=https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-elections-commissioner-casts-vote-at-polling-station-after-9-years-72649,%20https://economynext.com/sri-lanka-elections-commissioner-casts-vote-at-polling-station-after-9-years-72649/|access-date=2020-08-05|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。约82000名安全人员和6万多名医护工作者在选举期间戒备<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka : Over 82,000 security personnel deployed to ensure peaceful election in Sri Lanka|url=http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug04_1596558356CH.php|access-date=2020-08-05|website=www.colombopage.com|archive-date=2022-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220403061835/http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug04_1596558356CH.php}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Colombo Stock Exchange|可伦坡证券交易所}}于晚上12点30分提前关闭<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka : Colombo Stock Exchange to close early tomorrow for Election|url=http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug04_1596565579CH.php|access-date=2020-08-05|website=www.colombopage.com|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806171754/http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug04_1596565579CH.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 出口民调观点 ==
