选举违规行为监测中心指，根据调查，约有340起与选举违规有关的小事件，其中约167起为非法竞选、59起为恐吓、24起为非法海报展板，另有部分涉及违反健康指引。人民自由联盟所受投诉最多，约161起，其次是团结—人民力量，有40起，之后是统一国民党，有18起<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-06|title=SLPP leads the race in Sri Lanka’s election law violations|url=https://economynext.com/slpp-leads-the-race-in-sri-lankas-election-law-violations-72698,%20https://economynext.com/slpp-leads-the-race-in-sri-lankas-election-law-violations-72698/|access-date=2020-08-06|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

=== 操纵意图 ===
代表{{tsl|en|Tamil National Alliance|泰米尔国民阵线}}的贾夫纳选区参选人{{tsl|en|M. A. Sumanthiran|M·A·苏曼西兰}}被指在优先次序选票点票期间存在不当行为，在选举结束后坐在点票中心内，而非按照规则在点票期间离开点票现场<ref>{{Cite web|title=TNA candidate demands investigation from EC and ITAK leader into controversial Jaffna recount {{!}} Tamil Guardian|url=https://www.tamilguardian.com/content/tna-candidate-demands-investigation-ec-and-itak-leader-controversial-jaffna-recount|access-date=2020-08-07|website=www.tamilguardian.com|archive-date=2022-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220406220530/https://www.tamilguardian.com/content/tna-candidate-demands-investigation-ec-and-itak-leader-controversial-jaffna-recount}}</ref>。苏曼西兰否认有关指控，指出点票工作在不同地点举行，再被带到选区主要的点票中心，最终结果需要经点票站现场的各党派代表确认和同意后公布。苏曼西兰透露点票期间他一直在家，没有出现在任何点票中心，只是在结果即将公布前前往宣布现场，其他参选人，包括沙希卡拉·拉维拉杰都在场，还跟选举主任交谈<ref>{{Cite web|title=Claims of foul-play over preferential vote count in Jaffna after late night recount {{!}} Tamil Guardian|url=https://www.tamilguardian.com/content/claims-foul-play-over-preferential-vote-count-jaffna-after-late-night-recount|access-date=2020-08-07|website=www.tamilguardian.com|archive-date=2022-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220409153304/https://www.tamilguardian.com/content/claims-foul-play-over-preferential-vote-count-jaffna-after-late-night-recount}}</ref>。沙希卡拉的女人和{{tsl|en|Nadarajah Raviraj|纳达拉·沙希卡拉}}谴责苏曼西兰打算犯规，可能意图操纵最终结果<ref>{{Cite web|last=Vyshnavy|date=2020-08-07|title=Raviraj accuses Sumanthiran of manipulating final results {{!}} Colombo Gazette|url=https://colombogazette.com/2020/08/07/raviraj-accuses-sumanthiran-of-manipulating-final-results/|access-date=2020-08-07|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220430073417/https://colombogazette.com/2020/08/07/raviraj-accuses-sumanthiran-of-manipulating-final-results/}}</ref>。

=== 统一国民党违规指控 ===
团结—人民力量指责统一国民党主席拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈试图通过优先次序投票保住他的席位，指统一党未能取得保住议会国民席位所需的至少5%的总票数<ref>{{Cite web|last=admin|date=2020-08-06|title=SJB claims Ranil making unlawful attempt to save seat {{!}} Colombo Gazette|url=https://colombogazette.com/2020/08/06/sjb-claims-ranil-making-unlawful-attempt-to-save-seat/|access-date=2020-08-07|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408011319/https://colombogazette.com/2020/08/06/sjb-claims-ranil-making-unlawful-attempt-to-save-seat/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-06|title=UNP lawyers attempting to count Ranil’s preferential votes, claims SJB|url=https://economynext.com/unp-lawyers-attempting-to-count-ranils-preferential-votes-claims-sjb-72722,%20https://economynext.com/unp-lawyers-attempting-to-count-ranils-preferential-votes-claims-sjb-72722/|access-date=2020-08-07|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

== 选举结果 ==
首批正式的选举结果于2020年8月6日下午陆续公布，从[[加勒区|加勒区]]的邮寄选票开始<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-06|title=First official result of parliamentary election released|url=https://www.newsfirst.lk/2020/08/06/first-official-result-of-parliamentary-election-released/|access-date=2020-08-06|website=Sri Lanka News – Newsfirst|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807105816/https://www.newsfirst.lk/2020/08/06/first-official-result-of-parliamentary-election-released/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

斯里兰卡人民自由联盟凭借59.09%的得票率在18个选区赢得145席，成为议会最大党，而他们主要的对手团结—人民力量则赢得23.90%的票数共54席<ref>{{Cite web|last=admin|date=2020-08-07|title=SLPP sweeps polls and secures 145 seats, SJB gets 54 {{!}} Colombo Gazette|url=https://colombogazette.com/2020/08/07/slpp-sweeps-polls-and-secures-145-seats-sjb-gets-54/|access-date=2020-08-07|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412201759/https://colombogazette.com/2020/08/07/slpp-sweeps-polls-and-secures-145-seats-sjb-gets-54/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-06|title=Sri Lanka election: Rajapaksa clan heading for landslide win in Lanka polls|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/world/sri-lanka-general-election-results-rajapaksa-6542242/|access-date=2020-08-07|website=The Indian Express|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807123318/https://indianexpress.com/article/world/sri-lanka-general-election-results-rajapaksa-6542242/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=France-Presse|first=Agence|date=2020-08-07|title=Sri Lanka's Rajapaksa brothers strengthen grip in landslide election win|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/07/sri-lankas-rajapaksa-brothers-strengthen-grip-in-landslide-election-win|access-date=2020-08-07|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807021502/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/07/sri-lankas-rajapaksa-brothers-strengthen-grip-in-landslide-election-win|dead-url=no}}</ref>人民自由联盟成功打出113个议席的多数门槛，在各个选区获得128席，在选举名单获得17席，共145席<ref>{{Cite news|last=Abi-Habib|first=Maria|date=2020-08-06|title=Sri Lanka Vote Hands Rajapaksa Family a Bigger Slice of Control|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/06/world/asia/sri-lanka-elections-rajapaksa.html|access-date=2020-08-07|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807001005/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/06/world/asia/sri-lanka-elections-rajapaksa.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。结果预计会进一步扩大拉贾帕克萨家族在斯里兰卡政界的影响力，人民自由联盟仅需要与其他小党派的5个席位进行合作，便可以达到启动宪法修改所需的多数席位门槛，其中部分席位可能会推翻2015年生效的多个修正案（包括增加议会和总理的角色、推行负责司法任命、警察、公共服务和选举进行的独立委员会）。拉贾帕克萨家族另有四人（除马欣达外）当选议员，包括马欣达儿子{{tsl|en|Namal Rajapaksa|纳马尔·拉贾帕克萨|纳马尔}}、哥哥{{le|查马尔·拉贾帕克萨|Chamal Rajapaksa|查马尔}}、他的儿子{{tsl|en|Shasheendra Rajapaksa|沙舍恩德拉·拉贾帕克萨|沙舍恩德拉}}和侄子{{tsl|en|Nipuna Ranawaka|尼普纳·拉纳瓦卡}}<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2020-08-09|title=Mahinda Rajapaksa sworn in as Sri Lanka's PM after record victory|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/mahinda-rajapaksa-sworn-sri-lanka-pm-record-victory-200809060134067.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809075738/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/mahinda-rajapaksa-sworn-sri-lanka-pm-record-victory-200809060134067.html|archive-date=2020-08-09|access-date=2020-08-09|website=Al Jazeera}}</ref>。得票和席位第二多的团结—人民力量有望去主要反对党统一国民党的位置，尽管该党是由国民党管理层产生分歧所成立的<ref>{{Cite web|title=SJB ready for main Opposition role {{!}} Daily FT|url=http://www.ft.lk/front-page/SJB-ready-for-main-Opposition-role/44-704255|access-date=2020-08-07|website=www.ft.lk|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807023909/http://www.ft.lk/front-page/SJB-ready-for-main-Opposition-role/44-704255|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-06|title=SJB claims it is now the country’s main Opposition Party|url=https://economynext.com/sjb-claims-it-is-now-the-countrys-main-opposition-party-72712,%20https://economynext.com/sjb-claims-it-is-now-the-countrys-main-opposition-party-72712/|access-date=2020-08-07|website=EconomyNext}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。隶属于{{tsl|en|Tamils in Sri Lanka|斯里兰卡泰米尔族|泰米尔少数族裔}}的政党失去多个议会，可能会削弱影响力，其对在[[联邦制|联邦国家]]实行自治的渴望可能会被外界质疑毫无进展。

选举委员会透露马欣达·拉贾帕克萨在选举期间获得了527,364票的最高排序票数<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sri Lanka : Election Commission releases preferential list of elected candidates, PM gets highest preferential votes|url=http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug07_1596783876CH.php|access-date=2020-08-08|website=www.colombopage.com|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809211401/http://www.colombopage.com/archive_20B/Aug07_1596783876CH.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

